---
const aboutImage =
  "https://res.cloudinary.com/dewf3zos0/image/upload/w_800,q_auto,f_auto/v1771190908/564612247_25379652824975888_8730496612735750076_n_j6ypor.jpg";
---

<section id="o-meni" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Slika -->
      <div class="fade-in order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src={aboutImage}
            alt="Kristjan Hočevar"
            class="w-full rounded-sm shadow-2xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <!-- Dekorativni okvir -->
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full border-2 border-accent/30 rounded-sm -z-10"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Besedilo -->
      <div class="fade-in order-1 md:order-2">
        <p
          class="text-accent tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-sm mb-3 font-semibold"
        >
          O meni
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
          Zgodbe,<br />spete z dušo
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Kristjan Hočevar je kantavtor, ki s svojo akusticno kitaro in
            glasom prica zgodbe, ki se dotaknejo. Njegove avtorske pesmi so
            iskrene, intimne in polne cutenj.
          </p>
          <p>
            Nastopa samostojno ali v družbi drugih glasbenikov. Doslej je izdal
            dve avtorski pesmi z videospotom, tretja pa je že na poti.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a
            href="#videospoti"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-accent hover:text-accent/80 transition-colors font-semibold"
          >
            Poslušaj pesmi
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-4 h-4"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
